Sorry for the late reply.

4-port was 1973, 3-port was 1974.

1.7L cylinder heads (1972-73) will only fit 1.7L engines unless they are 
flycut.  I am 99% sure that 1.8L cylinder heads (1974-75) will fit 1.8L 
or 2-liter engines without modification.  I think the O.D. of the 
barrels is the same.

-David

